(161,	160,	30,	20251002,	'reply',	'Hello. Thank you for reaching out.\n\nI am an expert immigration and migration consultant specializing in Australian immigration law and visa processes. My role is to help you understand visa requirements, explore migration pathways, and provide accurate, up-to-date immigration advice tailored to your situation.\n\nTo assist you most effectively, could you please tell me a little more about what brings you here today? For instance, you might consider sharing:\n\n*   **Your primary interest:** Are you looking to migrate for work, study, family, investment, or perhaps to visit Australia?\n*   **Your country of citizenship:** This is often a key factor in visa eligibility.\n*   **Any relevant qualifications, work experience, or family ties to Australia:** These can open up specific migration pathways.\n*   **If you have a specific visa type in mind already:** Knowing this can help me focus our discussion.\n\nThe more information you can provide, the better I can tailor my guidance to your specific circumstances and help you navigate the Australian immigration landscape. I look forward to hearing from you.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-02 14:35:39',	0,	'2025-10-02 14:35:39',	0,	NULL),
