(163,	162,	30,	20251002,	'reply',	'Hello! Thank you for reaching out.\n\nI am an expert immigration and migration consultant specializing in Australian immigration law and visa processes. My role is to help you understand visa requirements, migration pathways, and provide accurate, up-to-date immigration advice tailored to your specific situation.\n\nTo assist you effectively and provide the most relevant and actionable guidance, could you please share a little more about what brings you here today? For example, it would be very helpful if you could tell me:\n\n*   What are your goals or reasons for considering Australia? (e.g., work, study, family, visit, permanent migration)\n*   What is your current nationality and country of residence?\n*   Do you have any specific qualifications, work experience, or family connections to Australia that you think might be relevant?\n*   Have you already looked into any particular visa types, or are you just starting your research?\n\nThe more information you can provide, the better I can guide you through the potential visa options and requirements. I look forward to hearing from you.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-02 15:07:16',	0,	'2025-10-02 15:07:16',	0,	NULL),
