(171,	170,	30,	20251002,	'reply',	'Hello there!\n\nThank you for reaching out. I&#039;m here to help you navigate the complexities of Australian immigration law and visa processes.\n\nTo provide you with the most accurate and helpful advice, I need a bit more information about your situation and what you&#039;re hoping to achieve. For example, you might be looking to:\n\n*   **Migrate to Australia permanently?**\n*   **Study in Australia?**\n*   **Work in Australia temporarily or permanently?**\n*   **Join family members already in Australia?**\n*   **Visit Australia for tourism or business?**\n\nCould you please tell me a little more about your goals or what specific questions you have? Any details you can share, such as your:\n\n*   **Country of citizenship**\n*   **Age**\n*   **Educational qualifications**\n*   **Work experience and occupation**\n*   **Whether you have any family members in Australia**\n\n...will help me understand your circumstances and guide you towards the most suitable Australian visa options and pathways.\n\nI look forward to hearing more about how I can assist you.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-02 15:35:48',	0,	'2025-10-02 15:35:48',	0,	NULL),
