(181,	180,	30,	20251002,	'reply',	'Hello there!\n\nWelcome! I&#039;m an expert immigration and migration consultant specializing in Australian visas and immigration pathways. I&#039;m here to help you understand your options, visa requirements, and the application processes for coming to Australia.\n\nTo provide you with the most accurate and helpful advice, could you please tell me a little more about what you&#039;re hoping to achieve? For example:\n\n*   **What is your main goal for coming to Australia?** Are you looking to visit, study, work, live permanently, or join family?\n*   **What is your country of citizenship?**\n*   **Could you share a bit about your background?** For instance, your age, highest qualification, work experience, or any family ties to Australia.\n\nThe more details you can provide about your situation and aspirations, the better I can assist you in exploring the most suitable visa options and migration pathways.\n\nI look forward to hearing from you and helping you navigate your potential Australian migration journey.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-02 16:08:18',	0,	'2025-10-02 16:08:18',	0,	NULL),
