(185,	184,	30,	20251002,	'reply',	'Hello there!\n\nThank you for reaching out. As an expert immigration and migration consultant specializing in Australian immigration law and visa processes, I&#039;m here to help you navigate the complexities and understand your options.\n\nTo provide you with the most accurate, specific, and helpful advice, I&#039;ll need a bit more information about your situation and what you&#039;re hoping to achieve in Australia. Please feel free to tell me:\n\n*   **What is your main goal?** (e.g., do you wish to live and work permanently, study, visit, work temporarily, start a business, or sponsor a family member?)\n*   **What is your current nationality?**\n*   **Could you share a little about your background?** (e.g., your age, highest qualification, work experience, English language proficiency, and family situation).\n*   **Are there any specific Australian visas or pathways you&#039;ve already been researching or are interested in?**\n\nThe more details you can provide, the better I can assess your potential eligibility, outline relevant visa options, and guide you through the next steps. I&#039;m here to offer professional and empathetic support, so please don&#039;t hesitate to share your questions and circumstances.\n\nI look forward to hearing more from you!',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-02 16:13:13',	0,	'2025-10-02 16:13:13',	0,	NULL),
