(191,	0,	30,	0,	'ai',	'Hello there! Thank you for reaching out.\n\nI\'m here to help you navigate Australian immigration law and visa processes. To provide you with the most accurate and helpful advice, I need a little more information about your situation and what you\'re looking to achieve.\n\nPlease tell me:\n\n1.  **What is your main goal?** (e.g., to work in Australia, study, visit, join a partner, migrate permanently, invest, etc.)\n2.  **What is your country of citizenship?**\n3.  **Do you have any specific qualifications, skills, or work experience** that might be relevant?\n4.  **What is your approximate age?** (This can be important for some visa categories)\n\nOnce I have a better understanding of your circumstances, I can outline relevant visa options, requirements, and the general process involved.\n\nI look forward to assisting you.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-02 17:07:41',	0,	'2025-10-02 17:07:41',	0,	NULL),
