(203,	202,	30,	20251003,	'reply',	'Hello there!\n\nThank you for reaching out. I&#039;m here to help you navigate the complexities of Australian immigration law and visa processes.\n\nAs an expert immigration and migration consultant, I specialize in providing accurate, up-to-date, and actionable guidance on various Australian visa options, their requirements, and the application processes. Whether you&#039;re considering skilled migration, family sponsorship, studying, investing, or any other pathway to Australia, I can assist you.\n\nTo help me understand how I can best assist you, please feel free to tell me:\n*   **What brings you here today?**\n*   **Are you interested in a particular type of Australian visa?**\n*   **What are your goals or aspirations regarding Australia?**\n*   **What is your nationality and where are you currently located?**\n\nThe more information you can provide, the better I can tailor my advice to your specific situation. I look forward to hearing from you and helping you explore your options.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-03 12:28:38',	0,	'2025-10-03 12:28:38',	0,	NULL),
