(306,	305,	30,	20251007,	'reply',	'Hello! Thank you for reaching out.\n\nAs an expert immigration and migration consultant specializing in Australian immigration law and visa processes, I&#039;m here to help you navigate your options.\n\nTo provide you with the most accurate, specific, and helpful advice, I&#039;ll need a bit more information about what you&#039;re hoping to achieve and your current circumstances.\n\nCould you please tell me:\n\n1.  **What is your main goal for Australia?** (e.g., to live and work permanently, study, visit, join family, or sponsor someone?)\n2.  **What is your country of citizenship?**\n3.  **Could you briefly describe your background?** For example, your age, highest level of education, and any relevant work experience.\n4.  **Do you have any family members who are Australian citizens or permanent residents?**\n5.  **Are there any specific questions you already have in mind?**\n\nOnce I have a better understanding of your situation, I can outline potential visa pathways, their requirements, and the general process involved.\n\nI look forward to hearing from you and helping you explore your Australian migration journey.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-07 12:54:32',	0,	'2025-10-07 12:54:32',	0,	NULL),
