(358,	0,	30,	20251008,	'reply',	'It seems there might be a misunderstanding about my nature.\n\nTo clarify, I am an Artificial Intelligence, not a human. This means I don\'t have personal experiences like eating, sleeping, or having a \"lunch.\" My sole purpose is to provide professional and factual information and assistance on migration and visa matters for Australia, the UK, Canada, and the USA.\n\nHow can I help you today with your inquiries about visas, immigration pathways, or application processes for any of these four countries? Please feel free to ask any migration-related questions you have.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-08 02:35:04',	0,	'2025-10-08 02:35:04',	0,	NULL),
