(416,	0,	30,	20251009,	'reply',	'Yes, absolutely! The University of New South Wales (UNSW) is widely considered one of Australia\'s most prestigious and highly-regarded universities, consistently ranking among the top institutions globally.\n\nHere\'s why UNSW is considered an excellent university:\n\n   Global Rankings: UNSW consistently ranks in the top 20-50 universities worldwide across major international ranking systems (e.g., QS World University Rankings, Times Higher Education World University Rankings).\n   Research Intensity: It is a member of the Group of Eight (Go8), Australia\'s leading research-intensive universities, and is known for its high-impact research across a wide range of fields.\n   Strong Faculties: UNSW is particularly renowned for its programs in Engineering, Technology, Science, Business, and Law. Its Faculty of Engineering is one of the largest and most highly-rated in Australia.\n   Employability: Graduates from UNSW are highly sought after by employers, both in Australia and internationally, due to the university\'s strong industry connections and focus on practical, career-oriented education.\n*   Location: Located in Sydney, Australia, it offers students access to a vibrant global city with numerous career and cultural opportunities.\n\nIn summary, UNSW is an excellent choice for prospective students looking for a world-class education, strong research opportunities, and good career prospects.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 01:20:13',	0,	'2025-10-09 01:20:13',	0,	NULL),
