(428,	0,	30,	20251009,	'reply',	'That\'s a great question! As an AI, I don\'t have a physical location or a \"where\" in the traditional sense. I exist on computer servers and operate virtually.\n\nMy purpose is to provide you with expert information and assistance regarding migration and visa pathways for Australia, the UK, Canada, and the USA, no matter where you are in the world.\n\nSo, how can I help you today with your study, work, or migration plans for any of these countries?',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 01:22:11',	0,	'2025-10-09 01:22:11',	0,	NULL),
