(430,	0,	30,	20251009,	'reply',	'Okay, \"study\" is a fantastic goal, and it\'s often an excellent pathway to international experience and even potential migration!\n\nTo help me give you the most relevant information about studying in Australia, the UK, Canada, or the USA, could you please tell me a bit more about what you\'re looking for?\n\nFor example, could you share:\n\n1.  Which country are you most interested in for study? (Australia, UK, Canada, or USA, or are you open to suggestions?)\n2.  What level of study are you aiming for?\n       Undergraduate (e.g., Bachelor\'s degree)\n       Postgraduate (e.g., Master\'s degree, PhD)\n       Vocational or short courses\n       English language courses\n3.  What field or subject area are you interested in studying? (e.g., Engineering, Business, IT, Health Sciences, Arts, Education, etc.)\n4.  What is your highest level of education completed so far? (e.g., High School Diploma, Bachelor\'s Degree, Master\'s Degree)\n5.  Are you also interested in potential post-study work rights or pathways to permanent residency after your studies?\n\nOnce I have a better understanding of your goals, I can provide detailed information on suitable universities, visa requirements, application processes, and potential migration outcomes.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 01:23:01',	0,	'2025-10-09 01:23:01',	0,	NULL),
