(472,	0,	30,	20251009,	'reply',	'Thank you for providing \"study.\"\n\nTo ensure I give you the most relevant information, could you please clarify:\n\n1.  Are you providing your educational background details to help me assess your potential eligibility for the Australian Temporary Skill Shortage (TSS) visa (subclass 482), as requested previously?\n       If yes, please provide the specific details:\n           Highest qualification: (e.g., Bachelor\'s Degree, Master\'s Degree, Diploma, Trade Qualification)\n           Field of study: (e.g., Electrical Engineering, Nursing, IT, Hospitality Management)\n           Country and institution: Where did you obtain this qualification? (e.g., University of Sydney, Australia; XYZ College, India)\n\n2.  Or are you now interested in exploring visa options specifically for studying in Australia, the UK, Canada, or the USA?\n    *   If yes, please let me know which country you are interested in.\n\nOnce I have this clarification, I can proceed accordingly!',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 05:26:15',	0,	'2025-10-09 05:26:15',	0,	NULL),
