(474,	0,	30,	20251009,	'reply',	'Hi there! Welcome back.\n\nI\'m ready to assist you further.\n\nTo recap, we were trying to clarify if \"study\" refers to:\n\n1.  Your educational background (highest qualification, field of study, country/institution) for the purpose of assessing your eligibility for the Australian Temporary Skill Shortage (TSS) visa (subclass 482), as per my earlier request.\n       If so, please provide those details!\n\n2.  Or if you are now interested in exploring study visa options for a specific country (Australia, UK, Canada, or USA).\n       If so, please let me know which country you\'d like to discuss.\n\nOnce you clarify, I can provide the most relevant and detailed information. I\'m here to help!',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 05:40:37',	0,	'2025-10-09 05:40:37',	0,	NULL),
(475,	0,	30,	20251009,	'ask',	'study',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 05:41:16',	0,	'2025-10-09 05:41:16',	0,	NULL),
(476,	0,	30,	20251009,	'reply',	'Thank you for repeating \"study.\" I understand you\'re trying to communicate something related to education or studying.\n\nTo ensure I provide you with the most accurate and helpful information, please help me understand what you mean by \"study\" in this context. There are two main ways I can interpret this:\n\nOption 1: You are providing details about your educational background for the Australian 482 visa assessment.\nIf this is the case, please provide the specific details of your education as I requested earlier:\n   Highest qualification: (e.g., Bachelor\'s Degree, Master\'s Degree, Diploma, Trade Qualification, etc.)\n   Field of study: (e.g., Electrical Engineering, Nursing, IT, Hospitality Management, etc.)\n   Country and institution: Where did you obtain this qualification? (e.g., University of Sydney, Australia; XYZ College, India)\n\nOption 2: You are interested in exploring visa options for studying in Australia, the UK, Canada, or the USA.\nIf this is what you mean, please tell me:\n   Which country are you interested in studying in? (e.g., \"I want to study in Canada,\" or \"Tell me about UK student visas.\")\n\nOnce you clarify your intent, I can proceed with the most relevant information for you.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 05:41:16',	0,	'2025-10-09 05:41:16',	0,	NULL),
