(486,	0,	30,	20251009,	'reply',	'Thank you for repeating \"study.\" I understand you are trying to provide information related to your education.\n\nSince your previous question was about the Australian Temporary Graduate visa (subclass 485) and I highlighted the Australian Study Requirement as the CRITICAL MISSING INFORMATION, I believe you are trying to provide those details.\n\nTo help me assess your eligibility for the 485 visa, please provide the following specific information about your studies in Australia:\n\n   What was your highest qualification obtained in Australia? (e.g., Master of Software Engineering, Bachelor of Information Technology, Diploma of Networking, etc.)\n   Which Australian institution did you study at? (e.g., University of Melbourne, RMIT University, TAFE NSW, etc.)\n   When did you complete your studies in Australia? (e.g., \"Graduated in December 2023,\" \"Completed in June 2024,\" etc.)\n   Was your course registered on CRICOS for a minimum of 92 weeks? (This is usually mentioned on your Confirmation of Enrolment (CoE) or academic transcript.)\n*   Did you complete this study while holding an eligible student visa?\n\nOnce I have these details, I can give you a much more definitive assessment of your eligibility for the 485 visa.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-09 08:29:14',	0,	'2025-10-09 08:29:14',	0,	NULL),
