(506,	0,	30,	20251010,	'reply',	'Thank you for providing \"university in UK.\"\n\nI understand that you might be interested in options related to studying in the UK, or perhaps the post-study work opportunities available after completing a university degree there.\n\nEarlier, I started to provide a comprehensive overview of UK visa types, which included study visas, but my response was cut off. I can certainly continue or restart that detailed explanation, focusing on study and post-study work routes if that\'s what you\'re interested in.\n\nTo ensure I provide the most relevant information for you, please clarify:\n\n1.  Are you interested in studying in the UK (e.g., specific courses, universities, student visa requirements)?\n2.  Are you interested in visa pathways for individuals who have already completed a university degree in the UK (e.g., Graduate Route visa, Skilled Worker visa after graduation)?\n3.  Would you like me to complete the general overview of UK visa types, including study, work, and other categories?\n\nAlternatively, please remember that we were in the middle of discussing Australian Employer Sponsored Visa pathways (specifically the Temporary Skill Shortage (TSS) visa (subclass 482) and the Employer Nomination Scheme (ENS) visa (subclass 186)) for your job offer as a Software Engineer in Australia.\n\nPlease let me know which direction you\'d like to take! I\'m here to assist with either UK or Australian visa inquiries.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-10 00:07:29',	0,	'2025-10-10 00:07:29',	0,	NULL),
