(510,	0,	30,	20251010,	'reply',	'Thank you for asking about your eligibility for the Australian Temporary Graduate visa (subclass 485).\n\nTo definitively determine if you can apply for the 485 visa, I still need specific details about your Australian study. The most critical factor is meeting the \"Australian Study Requirement.\"\n\nBased on our previous interactions, I understand you have a Master\'s degree and an IELTS score of 7, which are positive indicators. However, to confirm your eligibility, please provide the following:\n\n   Completion Date of Your Australian Study: When did you officially complete your Master\'s degree in Australia (e.g., month and year)? You must apply for the 485 visa within 6 months of your course completion.\n   CRICOS Registration Duration: Was your Master\'s degree registered on CRICOS for a minimum of 92 weeks? This detail is usually on your Confirmation of Enrolment (CoE) or academic transcript.\n*   Visa Held During Study: Did you complete your Master\'s degree while holding an eligible student visa (subclass 500)?\n\nWithout these specific details, I cannot provide a conclusive assessment. Please provide this information so I can advise you accurately on your 485 visa eligibility.',	'immigration',	1,	0,	'2025-10-10 01:03:59',	0,	'2025-10-10 01:03:59',	0,	NULL),
