(1,	0,	1,	'2022-03-25',	0,	'Wealthskey Immigration Classroom makes its grand debut!!!',	'&lt;p&gt;Ken Sir, the author of &quot;The Immigration Winner&#039;s Guide&quot;, teamed up with former anchor Zhang Wenzhuo to help immigrant friends solve the immigration regulations, tax regulations and post-immigration food issues that are of most concern to them. Everyone who is interested or has immigrated should not miss it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Hurry up and go to the Wealthskey Immigration Classroom website for free classes: http://immi-class.com&lt;/p&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'6eed1a44a205cf15b448bd26a80d2909',	0,	1,	1,	1,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 16:45:42',	1,	'2024-04-09 17:34:03',	0,	NULL),
(2,	0,	1,	'2022-03-25',	0,	'Wealthskey移民教室隆重登場!!!',	'&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;《移民贏家指南》作者Ken Sir夥拍前主播張文釆為移民朋友解決最關心嘅移民條例、稅例及移民後搵食問題。每個有興趣或已經移民嘅朋友都不可錯過。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;快啲去Wealthskey移民教室網站上免費堂先啦︰&lt;a class=&quot;x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1fey0fg&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; role=&quot;link&quot; href=&quot;http://immi-class.com/?fbclid=IwAR3t2fOkSfvHGP2mnHSmhFP_1ZBOCxLgv_SENZUrbdsGvwXFpsUd8RUqEUM_aem_AeoWdrUTZaZsJ1WjRqjR3uWZsW37Q3gV0IKEYps2SeTCuUVVQ8Q8F5v101WjI-vr-bIhn2geKMLLacM53vs9QnMC&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;http://immi-class.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'6eed1a44a205cf15b448bd26a80d2909',	0,	1,	2,	1,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 16:45:42',	1,	'2024-04-09 17:34:03',	0,	NULL),
(3,	0,	1,	'2022-03-25',	0,	'Wealthskey移民教室隆重登场!!!',	'&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;《移民赢家指南》作者Ken Sir伙拍前主播张文釆为移民朋友解决最关心嘅移民条例、税例及移民后搵食问题。每个有兴趣或已经移民嘅朋友都不可错过。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;快啲去Wealthskey移民教室网站上免费堂先啦︰&lt;a class=&quot;x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1fey0fg&quot; tabindex=&quot;0&quot; role=&quot;link&quot; href=&quot;http://immi-class.com/?fbclid=IwAR3t2fOkSfvHGP2mnHSmhFP_1ZBOCxLgv_SENZUrbdsGvwXFpsUd8RUqEUM_aem_AeoWdrUTZaZsJ1WjRqjR3uWZsW37Q3gV0IKEYps2SeTCuUVVQ8Q8F5v101WjI-vr-bIhn2geKMLLacM53vs9QnMC&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;http://immi-class.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'6eed1a44a205cf15b448bd26a80d2909',	0,	1,	3,	1,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 16:45:42',	1,	'2024-04-09 17:34:03',	0,	NULL),
(4,	0,	2,	'2022-04-07',	3,	'Canada will ban some foreigners from purchasing residential properties in the next two years',	'&lt;p&gt;Canada&#039;s new budget will be announced on Thursday. Sources indicate that the government will introduce new measures to restrict foreigners from purchasing residential properties locally.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Bloomberg News quoted Canadian government sources as saying that the authorities will ban most foreigners from purchasing residential properties there in the next two years, and will allocate billions of dollars to stimulate housing construction.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Foreigners who are prohibited from buying real estate do not include students, foreign workers, and foreigners with Canadian permanent residence status. Local media reported that the ban is targeted at people who leave Canada after buying a property and will not live there, leaving the property empty.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;In addition, the Canadian government also plans to allocate funds to build &quot;affordable&quot; housing and help local governments update their systems to speed up the construction of new buildings. It is expected that the total expenditure on housing policies in the next five years will reach tens of billions of Canadian dollars.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Canadian property prices are among the highest among developed regions in the world. In the past two years alone, housing prices have increased by 50%. In February this year, the price increase hit a record high.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Analysts believe that the new measures demonstrate Prime Minister Trudeau&#039;s determination to decisively curb property prices. They also reveal that the Canadian government is increasingly concerned about inflation and the political backlash caused by high property prices.&lt;/p&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'2e8fd6dc01f14b01771d657b7b2e8bf7',	0,	1,	1,	2,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:04:33',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:04:44',	0,	NULL),
(5,	0,	2,	'2022-04-07',	3,	'加拿大未來兩年將禁部分外國人購置住宅物業',	'&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;加拿大新一份財政預算案將於周四公布。消息指，政府將有新措施限制外國人在當地購置住宅物業。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;彭博通訊社引述加拿大政府消息人士指，當局將禁止大部分外國人未來兩年在當地購置住宅物業，同時會撥款刺激住屋建設，金額以十億美元計。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;被禁制買樓的外國人士不包括學生、外籍勞工，以及擁有加拿大永久居留資格的外國人。當地傳媒報道，禁令是針對買樓後離開加拿大、不會在當地生活、任由房產丟空的人。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;另外，加拿大政府亦計劃撥款興建「國民負擔得起」的房屋，並幫助地方政府更新系統，以便加快新樓興建進度，預料未來五年在房屋政策方面，開支總額達百億加幣。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;加拿大物業價格之高，在全球已發展地區當中數一數二，單是過去兩年，房價便上升了五成，今年二月的樓價漲幅更創下歷史新高。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;分析認為，新措施展示總理杜魯多果斷遏抑樓價的決心，另外亦揭示了加拿大政府對通脹以至高樓價所帶來的政治反彈越來越關注。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'2e8fd6dc01f14b01771d657b7b2e8bf7',	0,	1,	2,	2,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:04:33',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:04:44',	0,	NULL),
(6,	0,	2,	'2022-04-07',	3,	'消息指加拿大未来两年将禁部分外国人购置住宅物业',	'&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;加拿大新一份财政预算案将于周四公布。消息指，政府将有新措施限制外国人在当地购置住宅物业。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;彭博通讯社引述加拿大政府消息人士指，当局将禁止大部分外国人未来两年在当地购置住宅物业，同时会拨款刺激住屋建设，金额以十亿美元计。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;被禁制买楼的外国人士不包括学生、外籍劳工，以及拥有加拿大永久居留资格的外国人。当地传媒报道，禁令是针对买楼后离开加拿大、不会在当地生活、任由房产丢空的人。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;另外，加拿大政府亦计划拨款兴建「国民负担得起」的房屋，并帮助地方政府更新系统，以便加快新楼兴建进度，预料未来五年在房屋政策方面，开支总额达百亿加币。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;加拿大物业价格之高，在全球已发展地区当中数一数二，单是过去两年，房价便上升了五成，今年二月的楼价涨幅更创下歷史新高。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;contentTxt&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;分析认为，新措施展示总理杜鲁多果断遏抑楼价的决心，另外亦揭示了加拿大政府对通胀以至高楼价所带来的政治反弹越来越关注。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'2e8fd6dc01f14b01771d657b7b2e8bf7',	0,	1,	3,	2,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:04:33',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:04:44',	0,	NULL),
(7,	0,	3,	'2022-06-21',	3,	'Home prices in many areas of Toronto plummeted by more than $100,000',	'&lt;p&gt;According to the latest data released by the Greater Toronto Area Real Estate Board, in May this year, the median price in the Greater Toronto Area was $1.05 million, a 4.4% drop from a month ago (approximately $48,000). House prices in some areas have dropped by more than 100,000 yuan in one month.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Home prices have fallen the most in Caledon, just over an hour&#039;s drive from Toronto. The median property price in this area was $1.33 million in May, a $192,000 drop.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Oakville, now the most expensive home in Canada, had the second-largest decline in May, now at $1.4 million. It dropped sharply by NT$172,500 in one month, an 11% drop from the previous month.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;However, not all areas in the Greater Toronto Area are experiencing price declines.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The report points out that for example, the median price in the Adjala-Tosorontio area of ​​Simcoe County rose to $1.225 million in May, an increase of 8.9% in one month, or about $100,000. Bradford-W Gwillimbury also rose 6.2% during the same period.&lt;/p&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'e9c81cda379a7e01c33464fc56de1793',	0,	1,	1,	3,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:16:53',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:16:53',	0,	NULL),
(8,	0,	3,	'2022-06-21',	3,	'多倫多大批地區樓價暴跌過10萬',	'&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;據大多倫多地區房產局最新公佈的數據，今年5月份，大多區的中位價為105萬元，較一個月之前跌了4.4%（約計4萬8000元）。一些地區的房價在一個月之內降了超過10萬元。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;在距離多倫多一個多小時車程的Caledon地區房價跌幅最大。這個地方5月份的房產中位價為133萬，暴跌19萬2000元。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;現在加拿大房價最貴的Oakville在5月份的跌幅排在第二位，現為140萬。一個月內之內急跌17萬2500元，較前一個月跌了11%。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;不過也並不是大多倫多地區內的所有區域都出現價格下跌的情況。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;報告指出，例如Simcoe County內Adjala-Tosorontio地區在5月份的中位價升到122萬5000元，一個月內升了8.9%，大約10萬元。Bradford-W Gwillimbury同期也升了6.2%。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'e9c81cda379a7e01c33464fc56de1793',	0,	1,	2,	3,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:16:53',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:16:53',	0,	NULL),
(9,	0,	3,	'2022-06-21',	3,	'多伦多大批地区楼价暴跌过10万',	'&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;据大多伦多地区房产局最新公佈的数据，今年5月份，大多区的中位价为105万元，较一个月之前跌了4.4%（约计4万8000元）。一些地区的房价在一个月之内降了超过10万元。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;在距离多伦多一个多小时车程的Caledon地区房价跌幅最大。这个地方5月份的房产中位价为133万，暴跌19万2000元。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;现在加拿大房价最贵的Oakville在5月份的跌幅排在第二位，现为140万。一个月内之内急跌17万2500元，较前一个月跌了11%。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;不过也并不是大多伦多地区内的所有区域都出现价格下跌的情况。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;报告指出，例如Simcoe County内Adjala-Tosorontio地区在5月份的中位价升到122万5000元，一个月内升了8.9%，大约10万元。Bradford-W Gwillimbury同期也升了6.2%。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'e9c81cda379a7e01c33464fc56de1793',	0,	1,	3,	3,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:16:53',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:16:53',	0,	NULL),
(10,	0,	4,	'2022-07-13',	3,	'Canada ranks as the country most people in the world want to immigrate to',	'&lt;p&gt;According to Narcity, if you could live anywhere in the world, where would you choose? According to a new study, for many people around the world, the answer to that question is: Canada.&lt;br /&gt;Canada is also considered a welcoming country for immigrants, ranking high in terms of quality of life, economic freedom and education. Canadians, on the other hand, are clearly interested in moving elsewhere. Japan, which ranks second on the list, is also a country that many Canadians want to move to.&lt;br /&gt;The top 10 rankings are as follows:&lt;br /&gt;First place: Canada&lt;br /&gt;Second place: Japan&lt;br /&gt;Third place: Spain&lt;br /&gt;Fourth place: China&lt;br /&gt;Fifth place: France&lt;br /&gt;Tied for sixth place: T&amp;uuml;rkiye, South Africa&lt;br /&gt;Eighth place: India&lt;br /&gt;Ninth place: Australia&lt;br /&gt;Tied for 10th place: Greece, Fiji&lt;/p&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'e4ade3a6ab287468daf6bc7f3f226902',	0,	1,	1,	4,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:19:49',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:19:49',	0,	NULL),
(11,	0,	4,	'2022-07-13',	3,	'加拿大獲評為全世界人最想移民的國家',	'&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;據Narcity報導，如果你可以住在世界上的任何地方，你會選擇去哪裡？根據一項新的研究，對於全世界許多人來說，這個問題的答案是：加拿大。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;加拿大也被認為是一個歡迎外籍人士的移民國家，在生活質量、經濟自由和教育方面名列前茅。另一方面，加拿大人顯然也很有興趣搬到其他地方。在排行榜上位居第二名的日本也是不少加拿大人想要搬去的國家。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;前10的排名如下：&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第一名：加拿大&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第二名：日本&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第三名：西班牙&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第四名：中國&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第五名：法國&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;並列第六名：土耳其，南非&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第八名：印度&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第九名：澳大利亞&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;並列第十名：希臘，斐濟&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'e4ade3a6ab287468daf6bc7f3f226902',	0,	1,	2,	4,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:19:49',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:19:49',	0,	NULL),
(12,	0,	4,	'2022-07-13',	3,	'加拿大获评为全世界人最想移民的国家',	'&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;据Narcity报导，如果你可以住在世界上的任何地方，你会选择去哪里？根据一项新的研究，对于全世界许多人来说，这个问题的答案是：加拿大。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;加拿大也被认为是一个欢迎外籍人士的移民国家，在生活质量、经济自由和教育方面名列前茅。另一方面，加拿大人显然也很有兴趣搬到其他地方。在排行榜上位居第二名的日本也是不少加拿大人想要搬去的国家。&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;前10的排名如下：&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第一名：加拿大&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第二名：日本&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第三名：西班牙&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第四名：中国&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第五名：法国&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;并列第六名：土耳其，南非&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第八名：印度&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;第九名：澳大利亚&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;div dir=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;并列第十名：希腊，斐济&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'e4ade3a6ab287468daf6bc7f3f226902',	0,	1,	3,	4,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:19:49',	1,	'2024-04-02 18:19:49',	0,	NULL),
(13,	0,	5,	'2024-07-14',	1,	'The most expensive thing in the world | Hong Kong’s prices lead the four major immigration hotspots. Is the salary for 4 days not as good as working for 1 day in Sydney?',	'&lt;p&gt;The $90 butter incident in the UK has changed the public&#039;s perception of Hong Kong&#039;s price level. BossMind integrated some consumption levels in four immigration locations (Taiwan, London, Sydney and Vancouver) and found that prices in London, Sydney and Vancouver are relatively high, but wages are low. It&amp;rsquo;s not thin, even if you get the minimum wage it&amp;rsquo;s enough to live on.&lt;/p&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'd9841ef31f5b7068b27fc38999d943a3',	0,	1,	1,	5,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:25:35',	1,	'2024-04-09 17:33:46',	0,	NULL),
(14,	0,	5,	'2024-07-14',	1,	'貴絕全球｜港物價領先四大移民熱點 4日工資不及悉尼工作1天？',	'&lt;p&gt;英國90元牛油一事，扭轉大眾對香港物價水平觀念，BossMind整合了4個移民地點（台灣、倫敦、悉尼及溫哥華）部份消費水平，發現倫敦、悉尼及溫哥華物價水平偏高，但薪酬卻不薄，即使領取最低工資亦足夠生活。&lt;/p&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'd9841ef31f5b7068b27fc38999d943a3',	0,	1,	2,	5,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:25:35',	1,	'2024-04-09 17:33:46',	0,	NULL),
(15,	0,	5,	'2024-07-14',	1,	'贵绝全球｜港物价领先四大移民热点 4日工资不及悉尼工作1天？',	'&lt;p&gt;英国90元牛油一事，扭转大众对香港物价水平观念，BossMind整合了4个移民地点（台湾、伦敦、悉尼及温哥华）部份消费水平，发现伦敦、悉尼及温哥华物价水平偏高，但薪酬却不薄，即使领取最低工资亦足够生活。&lt;/p&gt;',	'',	'',	'',	'd9841ef31f5b7068b27fc38999d943a3',	0,	1,	3,	5,	1,	1,	'2024-04-02 18:25:35',	1,	'2024-04-09 17:33:46',	0,	NULL);
